Exercise 1:
1. Write The Commands To Perform Basic Arithmetic In R.
Program:
x&lt;-c(1,2,3,4,5,6)
y&lt;-c(4,5,3,9,7,9)
print(&quot;addition:&quot;)
print(x+y)
print(&quot;subtraction:&quot;)
print(x-y)
print(&quot;multipication:&quot;)
print(x*y)
print(&quot;division:&quot;)
print(x/y)
print(&quot;exponent:&quot;)
print(x^y)
print(&quot;modulus:&quot;)
print(x%%y)
Output:

